It's officially 2013 and how the time has gone by, Viktor is 6 months old and I'm about halfway through my deployment already to start thinking about what to so when I get back cuz it's officially this Is my last tour in the army.

Posted via LiveJournal app for iPad.

Ah haha I think I just found a faster way of doing this! This is good cuz the long way didnt inspire me to comment. Also this new layout, if new at all, interests me. But any how, I got an apartment up here and Lex will be moving up here in no time flat. In fact 4 March is her arrival date. I am excited. That is all since all my stuff is officially classified at the school house.

Everyone who knows me must call me on sunday the third if you would like to go to the beach so that i can get things straight. The party, so to speak, is on tuesday and is an all day thing. Call me at 4074889539
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/3556.html

I have eight days left! And by some weird twist of fate I lost my cell phone so I need everyone to call me at my other cell phone in order to get your numbers all over again! My other cell number is 4074889539. Call soon so plans for the party can be made!
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/3250.html

Okay so the beach thing wont work out cause of the damn weather the beaches are expected to see plenty of thunderstorms. Anyone have any idea of what else we could do. I have live 21 days before I drive to tampa and get ship out to soutch carolina.
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/2826.html

Any way Ive been finding it difficult to call people cause somes of us refuse to pick up so this is about the beach I am moving it to tuesday or thursday Im starting to tuesday since I have that day off. People for the love of god call me so we can set things straight. I now remember why I usually dont plan things. . .

Anyone else stuck doing a Senior Notebook?! Damn English, I'm so behind on the bloody thing. I have like fife days to do the whole bloody thing! I dont even have pics that I know of. I might, not sure. But Im pretty sure I don't anyone out there have pics of me I dont konw about, I know Anh has some she always does. . .

SO I WONT TEll YOU! Didnt suspect that one did ya! Ha! Any how just bored and I figured Id start doing this thing-a-ma-bober whenever I get the chance which may be often now. . . But for now I have nothing.

yeah, it's me, bri, updating for chris because his computer sucks. i'll speak in his point of view: allo loves! so hopefully if all goes according to plan, i'll be going to WP next year, because i refuse to go to boone or colonial. i also want to hang out with everyone before school starts, so if you can, id appreciate any comments with ideas/suggestions for what we could do. please note that my email address has been changed to Galamiesariyan@yahoo.com talk to you all later! ~chris by way of bri
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/2032.html

Yup, I'm still alive and kickin'. For the most part at least. Just really bored. Really, really bored. I got school, atleast. Am doing well in school. New friend too, she came up from florida only a few weeks ago. Came from kissimmee (spelling), in fact she was going to go to winter park before her mother disowned her. Would have been in a lot of anh's classes! Weird koinkydink! Names Malary, its cool. She and I are the only southern yankies in the school. Anyhow, my other big news is my cats are big now. That is all. Sorry, my life sucks at the moment, all though despite the suckyness Im still kind of happy.
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/1743.html

Ive done nothing, absolutely nothing, my life has no  anything. Its just there. Without event. I s[pend my days hoping funnyjokes.com sends me some jokes before I lose my mind. Someone give me some cheap Ideas!!!!!!!
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/1460.html
I have a baby now! It's a boy! We named him Dart! He's the cutest bloody thing I've ever seen! His little grey eyes! And he has nappy light hair!
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/1040.html

I may not be to this for a while not until I find my cat at least. Shana went missing this morning. They went to walk the dog and didnt know the cat was left loose in the living room. They left the door open and she walked out. I wouldnt be so worried had it not been that Shana is an indoor cat and has never been outside long enough to learn the lay of the land. I dont know what to do...
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/812.html

I have spent all bloody day shopping and getting small things in order, like letters. I have written everyone letters, and in some cases rewritten letters. I spent a good deal of today buying shoes too. Got two pairs, cost me a bundle too. Then I helped Brook choose some clothes. That was harder then I expected. Then I got a hair cut that took, two hours, can you believe that. Any how, I got home and am tired. That is all...
http://galamie-sariyan.livejournal.com/694.html

This is for all you girls who need some lovin' if you need some, go somewhere else cause I got Brookakin's. Secondly for all you girls at Winter Park High, I miss you, the whole lot of you! Sorry my keep in touch skills are beneath acceptable standards. I'll try harder. I love yall. Okay, for everyone else I don't know. Hey I'm Chris. Pleasure meetin' you. I'm the new guy. If I mess up in any little way, I apologize. It happens, in fact it may happen alot. so excuse me. I'll try harder. Pleasure meeting you.
